sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant SG as /skill-genesis
    participant Agent as skill-genesis (bg)
    participant FS as .ai-state/skill_genesis_reports/
    participant SGR as /skill-genesis-review
    participant CE as context-engineer
    participant Mem as remember MCP

    U->>SG: /skill-genesis (optional --since, --scope)
    SG->>Agent: Task(...) background
    SG-->>U: agent spawned; report will land at path

    Agent->>Agent: Phases 1-4 (scope, sources, dedup, triage)
    Agent->>FS: write SKILL_GENESIS_REPORT_<TS>.md (review_status: pending)
    Agent->>FS: append row to SKILL_GENESIS_LOG.md
    Agent-->>U: report ready (via PROGRESS.md)

    Note over U,FS: temporal gap — user dispositions when ready

    U->>SGR: /skill-genesis-review
    SGR->>FS: scan, find latest pending report
    SGR->>U: single AskUserQuestion multi-select (N proposals)
    U-->>SGR: dispositions (approve / reject / refine / defer)
    SGR->>FS: append rows to Disposition Log; update frontmatter
    SGR->>Mem: remember(...) for approved memory proposals

    SGR-->>U: surface skill/rule delegations; confirm?

    opt user spawns delegations now
        U->>CE: context-engineer with approved proposals
    end
